jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/04/06/1094521970_83:0:1057:548_1920x0_80_0_0_3e3cbf7438ec00adec860cc6d0b0e0ff.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 俄罗斯国防部</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">谢尔盖·列别杰夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_lebedev_sergey/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:s.lebedev@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据俄国防部测算，自保卫顿巴斯专项行动开展以来，俄共击落乌克兰飞机428架、直升机234架、坦克9218辆。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">国防部表示，俄罗斯武装部队使用巡航导弹对乌克兰存放外国设备和弹药的仓库进行了高精度打击。结果，乌克兰的大部分库存被销毁。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “昨晚，俄罗斯武装部队使用高精度远程海基和空基武器对敌人的储备和储存外国武器和硬件的大型仓库发动了集体打击。罢工的目的已经达到，”国防部在一份声明中说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110442643" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/russian-strike-eliminates-massive-stock-of-foreign-weapons-and-ammo-in-ukraine-1110442643.html?share-block=1110442645" data-title="“Last night, the Russian Armed Forces launched group strikes by high-precision long-range sea- and air-based weapons against the enemy&amp;#x27;s reserves and full-sized depots storing foreign armament and hardware. The purpose of the strike has been achieved,” the MoD said in a statement."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">预备队进入战区的行动也受阻。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯武装部队在 Kupyansk、Krasny Liman 和 Kherson 方向以及顿巴斯和扎波罗热地区成功作战，粉碎了基辅武装分子及其装备，包括尖端的美制火炮系统和苏联设计的苏式火炮系统-24架飞机。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当俄罗斯发起保护顿巴斯人民的特别军事行动时，西方国家加大了对基辅政权的军事支持，为其提供了最先进的装备。莫斯科官员一直警告说，此类举动会对危机产生不利影响，而且北约的武器，无论多么先进，最终都会被摧毁。本周，一枚俄罗斯 Kinzhal 导弹击中了位于基辅的美国爱国者导弹发射台——该防空系统曾被视为美国军事霸权的象征。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 16:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/russian-strike-eliminates-massive-stock-of-foreign-weapons-and-ammo-in-ukraine-1110442643.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/russian-strike-eliminates-massive-stock-of-foreign-weapons-and-ammo-in-ukraine-1110442643.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[BoE Admits 'Uncertain Outlook' for Inflation as UK Faces Wage-Price Spiral]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110441666" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/12/1110440544_0:0:2971:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_fa53fc3968c4eaaf0688edcb58227565.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1110440526" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/boe-admits-uncertain-outlook-for-inflation-as-uk-faces-wage-price-spiral-1110441666.html?share-img=1110440526"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / SUSANNAH IRELAND</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2023 年 3 月 31 日，在伦敦东部的水果和蔬菜市场，一个标牌显示了包括黄瓜在内的食品的英镑价格</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="A sign displays the price in pound sterling of food goods, including cucumbers, at a a fruit and vegetable market in stall east London on March 31, 2023 - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="2023 年 3 月 31 日，在伦敦东部的一个水果和蔬菜市场，一个标牌显示了包括黄瓜在内的食品的英镑价格" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/12/1110440544_0:188:2971:1859_1920x0_80_0_0_126516f2e778dcea7116b4c511855499.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/12/1110440544_0:188:2971:1859_640x0_80_0_0_2fd0658cf43137afa5bdc630e78ed8d9.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/12/1110440544_0:188:2971:1859_1280x0_80_0_0_a058722f8e8fbe0c866ec8b420ab7d4d.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/12/1110440544_0:188:2971:1859_1920x0_80_0_0_126516f2e778dcea7116b4c511855499.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / 苏珊娜爱尔兰</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Oleg Burunov - Sputnik International" title="奥列格布鲁诺夫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/09/0b/1080424846_0:0:2048:2048_100x100_80_0_0_3d7b461f8a98586fa3fe739930816aea.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">奥列格布鲁诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_burunov_oleg/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:o.burunov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">英国飙升的食品和非酒精饮料价格继续推动该国目前两位数的通货膨胀。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">英格兰银行行长安德鲁贝利首次承认英国央行正在努力应对英国的工资价格螺旋上升，因为他发誓要在必要时提高<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221215/bank-of-england-raises-uk-interest-rate-to-highest-level-in-14-years-1105491020.html" target="_blank">利率</a>以使通货膨胀率回到银行的 2% 目标。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>工资价格螺旋上升是一种宏观经济理论，表明工资上涨会增加可支配收入，增加对商品的需求并导致价格飙升。价格上涨增加了对更高工资的需求，从而导致更高的生产成本和价格进一步上涨的压力，从而形成概念螺旋。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">英国央行行长周三在伦敦举行的英国商会年会上表示，“（英国）核心通胀的一些强劲反映了能源价格上涨的间接影响。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “但它也反映了第二轮效应，因为我们看到的外部冲击与国内经济状况相互作用。随着总体通胀下降，这些第二轮效应不太可能像出现时那样迅速消失，”贝利指出.据他介绍，这些坚持的领域包括国内工资增长和价格设定。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110441666" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/boe-admits-uncertain-outlook-for-inflation-as-uk-faces-wage-price-spiral-1110441666.html?share-block=1110441829" data-title="&amp;quot;But it also reflects second-round effects as the external shocks we have seen interact with the state of the domestic economy. As headline inflation falls, these second-round effects are unlikely to go away as quickly as they appeared,&amp;quot; Bailey pointed out. According to him, these areas of persistence include domestic wage growth and price setting."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他承认，“未来通胀前景更加不确定，取决于工资和价格设定的持续程度。”贝利承诺，“[英国央行货币政策]委员会 (MPC) 将继续密切关注通胀压力持续存在的指标。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “我可以向你保证，货币政策委员会将在必要时调整银行利率，以使通胀在中期恢复到可持续目标，这符合其职权范围，”这位英国央行行长表示。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110441666" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/boe-admits-uncertain-outlook-for-inflation-as-uk-faces-wage-price-spiral-1110441666.html?share-block=1110441966" data-title="&quot;I can assure you that the MPC will adjust Bank Rate as necessary to return inflation to target sustainably in the medium term, in line with its remit,&quot; the BoE governor said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一家英国报纸就此回忆道，在过去的18个月里，英国央行多次表示，它正在努力阻止高能源和食品成本影响国内工资和物价的风险。据媒体报道，通过发表周三的讲话，这位银行行长“现在已经承认”英国央行“未能完成这项任务”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">贝利在 4 月份<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230328/consulting-company-uk-food-inflation-hits-record-high-of-175-1108866615.html" target="_blank">英国通胀</a>保持在两位数之后发表讲话，年价格上涨 10.1%，这增加了英国央行进一步加息的可能性，这是该银行传统上采取的应对这一问题的措施。英国的年通货膨胀率在 2022 年 10 月达到 11.1%，创下 41 年来的新高，随后几个月有所下降。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>这些事态发展是在 2021 年开始的英国生活成本危机中展开的，当时许多基本必需品的价格上涨速度开始快于家庭收入，导致实际收入直线下降。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">除了通货膨胀率飙升外， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230331/over-3-bln-ppe-items-disposed-by-uk-government-during-covid-pandemic-1108980607.html" target="_blank">COVID-19 大流行</a>和西方因其在乌克兰的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/russias-special-military-operation-in-ukraine-and-how-it-is-progressing-1105665248.html" target="_blank">特别军事行动</a>而对俄罗斯实施的制裁被认为是英国经济状况恶化的主要因素之一。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伦敦是<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230420/g7-mulls-outright-ban-on-most-exports-to-russia-as-sanctions-fall-flat-1109705615.html" target="_blank">反俄罗斯制裁</a>的最坚定支持者之一，反对和平解决<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230322/western-governments-must-prepare-for-long-term-conflict-amid-ukraine-crisis-scholz-warns-1108666325.html" target="_blank">乌克兰危机</a>，但结果是，英国人发现自己成为受全球经济动荡打击最严重的国家之一。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 15:45:24 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/boe-admits-uncertain-outlook-for-inflation-as-uk-faces-wage-price-spiral-1110441666.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/boe-admits-uncertain-outlook-for-inflation-as-uk-faces-wage-price-spiral-1110441666.html<category>经济</category><category>英国</category><category>英格兰银行</category><category>通货膨胀</category><category>特别行动</ca