pen-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Steven Senne</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Вкладчики у банка 硅谷 в штате Массачусетс</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Вкладчики у банка Silicon Valley в штате Массачусетс - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="Вкладчики у банка 硅谷 в штате Массачусетс" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0f/1108419606_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_42609e9689f82b3edb2d1efdc8d5d3dc.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0f/1108419606_0:161:3071:1888_640x0_80_0_0_4dc120afac1aff4274059d5447e379b0.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0f/1108419606_0:161:3071:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_a0570bfc0cfdf1f30c2e68356455f347.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/0f/1108419606_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_42609e9689f82b3edb2d1efdc8d5d3dc.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Steven Senne </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="James Tweedie - Sputnik International" title="詹姆斯·特威迪" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/08/1c/1080307270_0:3:397:400_100x100_80_0_0_7777393b9b18802f2e3c5eaa9cbcc612.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">詹姆斯·特威迪</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tweedie_james/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:j.tweedie@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">硅谷银行3月份的突然倒闭震惊了金融市场。 Larrea Wealth Management 首席执行官 Aquiles Larrea 表示，该银行的管理层在看到这家注定失败的行业贷方的“不祥之兆”时去寻找新投资者是“疯狂”还是“傲慢”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一位基金经理表示，硅谷银行 (SVB) 的高管在破产和纳税人资助的救助迫在眉睫之际向自己支付奖金是“犯罪行为”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这家科技行业银行的老板周三在参议员面前就该银行 3 月份<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230311/domino-effect-feared-after-collapse-of-silicon-valley-bank-as-first-republic-banks-shares-slump-1108292604.html" target="_blank">的倒闭</a>作证。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在 SVB 承认其国债投资组合因美联储加息以应对通货膨胀而贬值后，联邦政府被迫介入储户挤兑。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <strong>Aquiles Larrea</strong>告诉 Sputnik <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/executives-of-collapsed-banks-reveal-greed-before-congress--1110424122.html" target="_blank">，SVB 的高管们承认给自己发奖金是“有趣的”，</a>即使在银行即将资不抵债的“墙上写着”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “这是一起发生的边缘犯罪事件，”他强调说。 “对我来说，你可以在你的银行即将倒闭的时候去领取奖金，这太疯狂了。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110439855" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/silicon-valley-bank-execs-criminal-to-pay-themselves-bonuses-before-collapse-1110439855.html?share-block=1110442172" data-title="&quot;It's a borderline criminal thing that occurred,&quot; he stressed. &quot;It's insane to me that you can go take a bonus while your bank is about to go under.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我的一部分在想，你知道吗？如果我处于那个水平，我可能会想同样的事情，”拉雷亚说。 “并不意味着它是对的。这并不意味着你所做的没有后果。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">但是，他承认，“我认为他们不会看到任何后果，”并补充说：“你如何证明某人事先知道的事情？”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位财富基金经理表示，SVB 的倒闭是“对银行的一次很好的老式挤兑”，并采用了 21<sup>世纪</sup>的在线银行技术。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “人们忘记了银行挤兑并不是人们去银行说，我想把我所有的钱都拿出来，”拉雷亚解释道。 “他们现在正在网上以这种方式尽可能地提取他们的资金和储蓄。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他说 SVB 高管正在关注这些趋势并寻找“会支持我们 [或] 收购我们的人。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “这只是银行董事的疯狂行为或傲慢行为，”拉雷亚说，“表现得好像他们不知道发生了什么，而当......公众作为一个整体相信他们知道发生了什么在。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110439855" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/silicon-valley-bank-execs-criminal-to-pay-themselves-bonuses-before-collapse-1110439855.html?share-block=1110442173" data-title="That was &quot;just crazy behavior or arrogant behavior on the part of the banks directors,&quot; Larrea said, &quot;acting as if they didn't know what was going on, when... the public as a whole believes they knew what was going on.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><em><strong>如需对时事进行更深入的分析，请关注我们的 Sputnik 广播节目<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/radio_fault_lines/" target="_blank">Fault Lines。</a></strong></em></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 14:29:24 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/silicon-valley-bank-execs-criminal-to-pay-themselves-bonuses-before-collapse-1110439855.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/silicon-valley-bank-execs-criminal-to-pay-themselves-bonuses-before-collapse-1110439855.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>金融危机</category><category>硅谷银行倒闭</category><category>丹尼尔·拉扎尔</category><category>硅谷银行</category><category>金库</category><category>美国联邦储备银行</category><category>美联储</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch Russian Kamikaze Drone Zap Ukrainian Howitzer Into Oblivion]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110440938" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107250/35/1072503550_0:0:1225:623_1440x900_80_0_1_69e06cfd1a99485dfddc485dcdaab1c2.png?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1072503549" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/watch-russian-kamikaze-drone-zap-ukrainian-howitzer-into-oblivion-1110440938.html?share-img=1072503549"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 照片： <a href="https://twitter.com/russia_progress" title="@russia_progress">@russia_progress</a> /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯神风敢死队无人机原型</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Russian Kamikaze Drone prototype - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="俄罗斯神风敢死队无人机原型" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107250/35/1072503550_58:0:1166:623_1920x0_80_0_0_2e38ced74a1900b3ed9cccdfe01a95cc.png" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107250/35/1072503550_58:0:1166:623_640x0_80_0_0_8370d3e5e603bc49ead95869aa46f564.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107250/35/1072503550_58:0:1166:623_1280x0_80_0_0_4d8f1717de323fe21cfd1ead0a3eab6e.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107250/35/1072503550_58:0:1166:623_1920x0_80_0_0_2e38ced74a1900b3ed9cccdfe01a95cc.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片： <a href="https://twitter.com/russia_progress" title="@russia_progress">@russia_progress</a> / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">谢尔盖·列别杰夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_lebedev_sergey/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:s.lebedev@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">游荡弹药，在媒体中通常被称为神风敢死队无人机，是一种能够进行高精度外科手术式打击的智能射弹。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯武装部队搜出了乌克兰的 2S1 Gvozdika 自行火炮系统，并用高精度弹药摧毁了它。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">游荡弹药，通常被称为神风敢死队无人机或自杀式无人机，不仅仅是一种射弹，但并不完全是一种普通的无人机。根据定义，这种武器可以在目标区域徘徊或被动等待，寻找猎物并在目标被精确定位时进行攻击。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这种弹药可以进行强大的突袭，此外，神风敢死队无人机能够选择性瞄准——这意味着攻击可以在飞行过程中中止或重新定向。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="video"><div class="article__video"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="media__video"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/css/videoplayer/videoplayer.min.css?9fe0c0742"><div class="video-player " style="padding-top: 56.25%;" data-nosnippet=""><video id="video_1110437113" data-import-id="91964183" data-media-id="1110437113" data-articleid="1110440938" data-title="Russian loitering ammunition destroyed the Ukrainian self-propelled artillery system 2S1 Gvozdika" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/watch-russian-kamikaze-drone-zap-ukrainian-howitzer-into-oblivion-1110440938.html" data-next-autoplay="false" data-length="12" playsinline="true" poster="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/12/1110437149_0:0:971:546_600x0_80_0_0_15bce47e886c04a1bc8733c1514c2870.jpg" preload="none" class="video-js vjs-fluid" width="100%" height="100%"><p class="vjs-no-js">要观看此视频，请启用 JavaScript，并考虑升级到支持 HTML5 视频的网络浏览器</p></video><div class="video_info" data-customer-type="" data-media-id="1110437113" data-import-id="91964183" data-article-id="1110440938" id="video_info__1110437113" data-video-length="12" data-video-type="" data-video-file-size="1809026" data-ads=""></div></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©人造卫星</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">从技术上讲，巡航弹药填补了巡航导弹和军用无人机之间的空白。潜伏等待目标的能力使它们优于巡航导弹。然而，它们被称为自杀式无人机是有原因的——它们有一个内置的弹头，而且它们无法在攻击中幸存下来。但是，它们比常规战斗无人机便宜得多。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 14:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/watch-russian-kamikaze-drone-zap-ukrainian-howitzer-into-oblivion-1110440938.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/watch-russian-kamikaze-drone-zap-ukrainian-howitzer-into-oblivion-1110440938.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>2S1 格沃兹迪卡</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Russia's Upper House to Consider Denunciation of CFE Treaty on May 24]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110442405" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/03/16/1094071862_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_64701f58a2a7a3cc4a60da5bc061bd40.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1094071858" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/russias-upper-house-to-consider-denunciation-of-cfe-treaty-on-may-24-1110442405.html?share-img=1094071858"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Maria Devakhina</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">位于莫斯科 Bolshaya Dmitrovka 街的俄罗斯联邦联邦议会联邦委员会大楼。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="The building of the Federation Council of the Federal Assembly of the Russian Federation on Bolshaya Dmitrovka Street in Moscow. - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="位于莫斯科 Bolshaya Dmitrovka 街的俄罗斯联邦联邦议会联邦委员会大楼。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/03/16/1094071862_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_b2e89a619b34223e0d2b4d1511fc6101.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/03/16/1094071862_0:0:3072:1728_640x0_80_0_0_eb86a08ac9d31767e7c51fae46692edd.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/03/16/1094071862_0:0:3072:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_014f45a95743a97eff30764c6774a31f.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/03/16/1094071862_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_b2e89a619b34223e0d2b4d1511fc6101.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Maria Devakhina </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：根据议程，俄罗斯议会上院将于 5 月 24 日审议一项关于废除冷战最后几年签署的《欧洲常规武装力量条约》的法案周四公布的会议纪要。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 5月10日，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京向该国议会下议院提交了一份关于废止《中欧条约》的法律草案。 5月16日，众议院通过了一项关于退出该条约的法律，称该决定完全符合俄罗斯的国家利益。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> CFE 条约​​于 1990 年由 16 个北约成员国和 6 个华约成员国的代表在巴黎签署。该条约对欧洲主要类型的常规军事装备进行了限制，并规定销毁多余的武器。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 1999 年，在伊斯坦布尔举行的欧洲安全与合作组织 (OSCE) 峰会上签署了该条约的更新版本，以考虑到华沙条约的解散和北约的扩张。然而，改编版本仅得到俄罗斯、白俄罗斯、哈萨克斯坦和乌克兰的批准。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2007年，普京签署了一项法令，暂停该国参加2007年的CFE条约，直到北约国家批准适应协议并开始履行其在该文件下的承诺。与此同时，俄罗斯仍然是 CFE 条约​​的缔约国。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 14:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/russias-upper-house-to-consider-denunciation-of-cfe-treaty-on-may-24-1110442405.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/russias-upper-house-to-consider-denunciation-of-cfe-treaty-on-may-24-1110442405.html<category>俄罗斯</category><category>俄罗斯-北约摊牌</category><category>欧洲常规武装力量条约 (CFE)</category><category>北约扩张</category></item></channel></rss>